title: 1 YEAR OF ROTTENSWAP NFT DROP
body:
2 artists have been commissioned (Jen, @hahawomanchild and Amer, @Btc_minimalist on twitter) Total of 66 NFTs. You will vote here on the choice of NFT as your "ticket in the hat" to possibly win that NFT. This is the only way to be eligible, since it captured held ROT, staked and farming. 

Anyone who wants to win an NFT has to vote. We will use quadratic voting, so you can spread your bet across multiple NFTs as you wish. Preference may be given to larger holders for randomized selections of the most rare NFTs. This is all open and up for debate.

The drops will happen randomly throughout the month of October. If you want to have input, change things up or add your own generative art to the mix, visit https://t.me/rottenswap and let us know

This NFT drop will contain rarity traits with some NFTs more rare than others.

Proposed attributes: 

      "trait_type": "Name",
      "trait_type": "Clothes",
      "trait_type": "Hand",
      "trait_type": "Background",
      "trait_type": "Accessory",
      "trait_type": "Hair",
      "trait_type": "Skin",
      "trait_type": "Face",
